<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
<title>Support ST-IU</title>

<style>
body{
  font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,"Segoe UI",sans-serif;
  background:#08111f;
  color:white;
  margin:0;
  padding:40px;
}
.wrap{
  max-width:800px;
  margin:auto;
}
.card{
  background:#111a33;
  padding:30px;
  border-radius:20px;
  margin-top:20px;
  border:1px solid rgba(122,162,255,0.16);
}
.btn{
  display:inline-block;
  padding:14px 22px;
  border-radius:12px;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-weight:600;
  margin-top:10px;
}
.paypal{
  background:#0070ba;
  color:white;
}
.vipps{
  background:#ff5b24;
  color:white;
}
.qr{
  max-width:240px;
  margin-top:15px;
  border-radius:14px;
}
p{
  color:#c8d4f0;
  line-height:1.6;
}
h1,h2,h3{
  margin-top:0;
}
code{
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  padding:4px 8px;
  border-radius:8px;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="wrap">

<h1>Support ST-IU</h1>

<p>
ST-IU is an independent AI research and development project.
If you want to support the work, you can donate below.
</p>

<div class="card">
  <h2>Donate with Vipps</h2>
  <p>Vipps number:</p>
  <h3>45867897</h3>
  <p>You can also scan the QR code if you place it at <code>public/vipps.png</code>.</p>
  <img src="/vipps.png" class="qr" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h2>Donate with PayPal</h2>
  <a class="btn paypal"
     href="https://paypal.me/punktump"
     target="_blank"
     rel="noreferrer">
     Donate with PayPal
  </a>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
